text: "Stay the Night" is an electro house and Dance pop song by Russian-German electronic music producer Zedd featuring vocals from Hayley Williams of Paramore. It was released on September 23, 2013.https://web.archive.org/web/20130913085916/http://www.amazon.com/Night- featuring-Hayley-Williams-Paramore/dp/B00EVP8OKI It is from the deluxe version of Zedd's debut studio album, Clarity. ==References== Category:2013 songs
title: Stay The Night (Zedd song)
